snippet.title: Rise of Humanity - Cinematic teaser trailer
snippet.description:
Gather, upgrade and combine cards, recruit new heroes as others meet their unfortunate demise and discover new strategies by completing missions in an attempt to stop the remnant of project Hivemind. 

Rise of Humanity is a turn-based strategy deckbuilding cardgame, coming to Steam in Q1 2021.

Wishlist now! https://store.steampowered.com/app/1048530/Rise_of_Humanity/
